@{b}Other peoples comments on DiamondBOX:@{ub}

    Since the initial public launch of DiamondBOX in 2000, I've recieved a number of positive mails from several Amigans around the world. This kind of feedback is an invaluable motivational factor, and it makes good reading on those long winter nights...

